Cheetah, I



Fortunately we arrived at the cheetah viewing area just before feeding time; this pair of cheetahs spent most of the rest of their time lounging out of site behind a hill watching the hoofstock. Their trainer fed them ground goat, almost from his hand.
Taken Sunday, October 06, 2002, 01:31:36pm.  Original image size: 3072x2048, 7.2Mb
